  <div id="text-content_48db8cb2-a28c-42a2-a6ee-08a25ca5bd12" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Grades</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-gradebook-settings" data-step-uuid="dd568e55-e8dd-45e4-b9de-465cb59e5b5b">
